        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> rice vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>cucumber salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
